e template tips",data=2},{description=Lg and "无" or "None",data=0},},default=1,},{name="refine_with_skin",label=Lg and "物品皮肤" or "Item with skin",hover=Lg and "在箱子中放入\"带有皮肤的模板\",得到对应皮肤的物品" or "Put the \"template with skin\" into the chest to get the items with corresponding skin",options={{description=Lg and "是" or "Yes",hover=Lg and "确保你确实拥有此皮肤" or "Make sure you already have this skin",data=true},{description=Lg and "否" or "No",data=false},},default=true,},{name="refine_by_minisign",label=Lg and "学习小木牌" or "Learn from minisign",hover=Lg and "在箱子中放入画好的小木牌,按照小木牌精炼" or "Put a painted \"minisign\" into the chest and refine according to \"minisign\"",options={{description=Lg and "否" or "No",data=0},{description=Lg and "是" or "Yes",data=1},{description=Lg and "仅" or "Only",hover=Lg and "只精炼小木牌上的内容" or "Refine only according to the picture on minisign",data=2},},default=1,},}